                "html": "<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: flex; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(216, 156, 246); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: inline; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">本文背景</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">悬疑文通常充满神秘感，作者会故意藏起一些信息，通过线索逐步揭开真相。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">不少小伙伴直接用 AI 写悬疑文，结果一开始就被 AI 坑了，气得不行。那 AI 到底能不能帮我们写悬疑文呢？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">我想起读过的《悬疑小说创作指导》，书里介绍了独特创作方法，带着大家经历悬疑小说创作过程。我借鉴书里思路，弄了一套悬疑小说创作提示词。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/64639/08d046c0-111a-4fdb-bf70-70fe84f1ed7d.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(153, 153, 153, 0.3) 2px 4px 8px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">书里说，悬疑故事其实是两套。一套是水下的故事，也就是案件实际咋发生的，凶手为啥作案、咋作案，有哪些人参与，案发时有啥相关人物等。另一套是读者看到的故事，主角抓线索解谜。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">AI 写悬疑文不行，很多时候是因为它既知道第一套故事信息，又从第二套故事角度写，就乱了。我的办法是让 AI 构思第一套故事，帮作者理清水下的故事，让作者知道案件咋发生。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">第二套故事另开会话，按常规流程完善就行（这里不展开讨论）。作者心里有数案件细节，别一开始就把信息给 AI，自己知道后指导 AI 创作。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: flex; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(216, 156, 246); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: inline; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">测试效果</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">老规矩，还是先看看提示词的效果吧。我用这套提示词测试<strong style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">国产Kimi、智谱清言、天工AI、国外Claude、Gemini</strong>，我发现这套提示词写出的小说，国内和国外的效果竟然差不多，大家可以分辨一下哪套是国内、哪套是国外的？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">两篇小说我都是围绕一个主题开始写，其中都是和AI交互了八次才开始撰写第一章节。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">主题</strong>是：<em style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213); font-style: italic; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">某黑医院暗中做人体器官的交易</em> 。要求是<strong style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">2万字</strong>以上</p> \n<h5 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">版本一</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h5> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(216, 156, 246); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(244, 238, 255); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">第一章：失踪的弟弟</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟的手指在键盘上飞快地敲击着，他的眼睛紧盯着电脑屏幕上的新闻报道。他是一名记者，但他现在正在调查的，却是他自己的家事。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“张伟，你弟弟的事情怎么样了？”同事小李走过来，关切地问道。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟抬起头，他的眼中满是疲惫：“还是没有什么进展，医院那边一直说浩浩是自己离开的，但我不信。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">小李皱了皱眉：“我也觉得不对劲，‘希望之光’医院的口碑一直很好，怎么会出这种事？”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟叹了口气：“我不知道，但我一定要找到他。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">夜幕降临，张伟独自一人来到了“希望之光”医院。医院的灯光昏暗，走廊里弥漫着消毒水的味道。他的脚步声在空旷的走廊里回响，显得格外孤单。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">他来到了弟弟张浩的病房前，推开门，病房里空无一人，只有一张床，床上的被子凌乱地堆在一角。张伟的心中涌起一股莫名的焦虑，他走到床边，伸手摸了摸被子，还是温的。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“浩浩，你到底去哪了？”张伟喃喃自语，他的声音在空荡荡的病房里回荡。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">突然，他的手机响了起来，是一条短信。他打开一看，是一串陌生的号码：“想要知道你弟弟的下落，就来医院的地下室。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟的心跳加速，他立刻冲出了病房，沿着楼梯一路向下，来到了地下室的入口。门紧闭着，他深吸了一口气，推开了门。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">地下室里昏暗而潮湿，只有几盏昏黄的灯泡在头顶摇晃。张伟小心翼翼地往前走，他的脚步声在空旷的空间里回荡，显得格外刺耳。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“你是谁？你知道我弟弟在哪？”张伟大声喊道，他的声音在地下室里回荡。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">没有人回答，只有回声。张伟的心中充满了不安，他继续往前走，直到他看到了一个身影，一个穿着白大褂的身影。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“你是谁？”张伟警惕地问道。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">那个人转过身，是李明，张浩的主治医生。他的脸上带着一种复杂的表情，既有愧疚，也有决绝。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“张伟，我知道你在找你弟弟。”李明的声音低沉而沙哑，“但我不能告诉你他在哪。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟的眼中闪过一丝怒火：“你知道什么？告诉我！”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">李明摇了摇头：“我只能说，你弟弟卷入了一些他不应该卷入的事情。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟的拳头紧紧地握了起来：“你是在威胁我吗？”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">李明叹了口气：“不，我只是在告诉你事实。有些事情，你还是不知道的好。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">张伟的眼中闪过一丝坚定：“我不会放弃的，我会找到我弟弟，不管付出什么代价。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">他转身离开了地下室，他的脚步坚定而有力。他知道，这将是一场艰难的战斗，但他已经准备好了。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<h5 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">版本二</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h5> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(216, 156, 246); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(244, 238, 255); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">第一章：死里逃生</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">夜色如墨，暴雨如注。城市的灯火在雨幕中显得朦胧而遥远，救护车的尖叫声划破了夜的宁静。林锐躺在车厢里，胸口像是被巨石压着，每一次呼吸都像是在与死神搏斗。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“坚持住，林先生，我们马上就到医院了！”护士的声音在耳边焦急地响起，她的手紧紧握着林锐的手，试图传递一丝安慰。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">林锐的意识在模糊与清醒之间摇摆，他感觉自己像是被拖入了一个黑暗的漩涡。他的心脏，那个曾经强劲跳动的心脏，现在却像是一台即将报废的机器，每一次跳动都伴随着剧烈的疼痛。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">终于，救护车停在了医院门口，林锐被迅速推进了急诊室。手术室的灯光刺眼，医生和护士忙碌的身影在眼前晃动，林锐的意识开始模糊。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“准备手术，心脏移植！”主刀医生的声音冷静而坚定。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">在麻醉药效的作用下，林锐的世界陷入了一片黑暗。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">一个月后，阳光透过病房的窗户洒在林锐的脸上，他缓缓睁开眼睛。一切都很安静，只有心电监护仪的“嘀嗒”声在耳边规律地响起。他感觉到胸口有一种异样的沉重，那是新心脏的存在。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“你醒了。”一个温柔的声音响起，是他的主治医生，李医生。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">林锐点了点头，声音沙哑：“我…还活着。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">李医生微笑着：“是的，你很幸运。心脏移植手术非常成功。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">林锐试图坐起来，但身体还很虚弱：“谢谢您，李医生。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">李医生帮他调整了一下枕头，让他更舒服一些：“现在你需要休息，不要想太多。”</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">就在这时，林锐的脑海中突然闪过一个画面，一个年轻人的脸，他感到一阵莫名的熟悉和恐惧。他摇了摇头，试图将这个画面赶走。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“怎么了？”李医生关切地问。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“没什么，可能是药的副作用。”林锐勉强笑了笑，但他知道，那不是普通的副作用。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">晚上，林锐再次梦到了那个年轻人。他在一片浓雾中奔跑，脸上写满了恐惧和绝望。林锐想要追上去，但他的脚步却像是被什么东西牢牢地束缚住，无法移动。他大声呼喊，但声音却在喉咙里消失。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">醒来时，林锐的额头上布满了冷汗。他知道，这个梦不同寻常，似乎在告诉他一些他必须去探寻的真相。他望着窗外，城市的灯光在夜色中闪烁，他的心中涌起一股决心。</p> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“我必须找出答案。”林锐自言自语，尽管他的身体还很虚弱，但他的眼神中却闪烁着坚定的光芒。他不知道这条路会通向何方，但他知道，他必须走上这条路。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<h5 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">提示词：</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h5> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(216, 156, 246); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(244, 238, 255); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; dis